Growing coily, kinky and afro-textured hair can be challenging:

Have you ever felt like you hair stops growing past a certain length?
Have you ever wished you didn't have to wait several years to have hair growth past your bra strap?
Do you ever feel like no matter what you do, your hair is always dry and brittle?
Do you struggle with retaining length?
Is your hair dull and lacking shine?

Well picture this:

How would you feel about the possibility of doubling your hair growth every month?
how about retaining the length you worked so hard for?
Or learning tips on how to keep you hair soft and shiny for beautiful hairstyles?

This book is a black hair care and natural hair care reference that teaches you methods on how to grow hair long, retain length and maintain healthy beautiful hair.
